"816","<BODY>I, Timothy Taggart, certify that:<BR><BR>1. I have reviewed this report on"
"817","Form N-SAR of American Growth Fund, Inc.;<BR><BR>2. Based on my knowledge, this"
"818","report does not contain any untrue statement of a material fact or omit to state"
"819","a material fact necessary to make the statements made, in light of the"
"820","circumstances under which such statements were made, not misleading with respect"
"821","to the period covered by this report;<BR><BR>3. Based on my knowledge, the"
"822","financial information included in this report, and the financial statements on"
"823","which the financial information is based, fairly present in all material"
"824","respects the financial condition, results of operations, changes in net assets,"
"825","and cash flows (if the financial statements are required to include a statement"
"826","of cash flows) of the registrant as of, and for, the periods presented in this"
"827","report;<BR><BR>4. The registrants other certifying officers and I are"
"828","responsible for establishing and maintaining disclosure controls and procedures"
"829","(as defined in rule 30a-2(c) under the Investment Company Act) for the"
"830","registrant and have:<BR><BR>a) designed such disclosure controls and procedures"
"831","to ensure that material information relating to the registrant, including its"
"832","consolidated subsidiaries, is made known to us by others within those entities,"
"833","particularly during the period in which this report is being prepared;<BR><BR>b)"
"834","evaluated the effectiveness of the registrants disclosure controls and"
"835","procedures as of a date within 90 days prior to the filing date of this report"
"836","(the Evaluation Date); and<BR><BR>c) presented in this report our conclusions"
"837","about the effectiveness of the disclosure controls and procedures based on our"
"838","evaluation as of the Evaluation Date;<BR><BR>5. The registrants other certifying"
"839","officers and I have disclosed, based on our most recent evaluation, to the"
"840","registrants auditors and the audit committee of the registrants board of"
"841","directors (or persons performing the equivalent functions):<BR><BR>a) all"
"842","significant deficiencies in the design or operation of internal controls which"
"843","could adversely affect the registrants ability to record, process, summarize,"
"844","and report financial data and have identified for the registrants auditors any"
"845","material weaknesses in internal controls; and<BR><BR>b) any fraud, whether or"
"846","not material, that involves management or other employees who have a significant"
"847","role in the registrants internal controls; and<BR><BR>6. The registrants other"
"848","certifying officers and I have indicated in this report whether or not there"
"849","were significant changes in internal controls or in other factors that could"
"850","significantly affect internal controls subsequent to the date of our most recent"
"851","evaluation, including any corrective actions with regard to significant"
"852","deficiencies and material weaknesses.<BR><BR>Date: 09/25/2010<BR><BR>/s/"
